Changed display system to match new property system + added name tag to properties + added animation classes
Added Vector2 to hold coordinates + put resource loading inside abstract class instead of being manual + prepared field for ImageFactory and Filters
Added Snake game to examples + integrated registration to GameObject + reorganized Resource folder
Added animation and sprite atlas systems
Added alpha rendering, rotations and lerp translations
